## SBA Lending Marketplaces

SBA 7(a) loans currently run approximately 9.5–12% APR (Prime + 2.0–4.25% depending on loan size). SBA 504 CDC debenture rates are fixed at approximately 5.5–7% for the 40% debenture portion. These marketplaces match businesses to SBA Preferred Lenders with a single application. See the [SBA Loans Guide](/guides/sba-loans/) and [SBA Loan Calculator](/tools/sba-loan-calculator/).

| Provider | Product Page | Notes |
